Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, section 1, 2c | Description :6 months after effective date hire an independent qualified consultantfor conducting regular inspections (spot checks/operation and audits) | Due Date :04-Feb-2010

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, section 1, A 3 | Description :60 days after effective date an MOU between Planning Commission andBISP will be signed regarding implementation of component 4 | Due Date :05-Oct-2009

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, section 1, A. 4. a | Description :Commencing on July 31, 2009 prepare for Bank concurrence theannual implementation plan to be implemented during the respective fiscal | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, section 3, E 1 | Description :4 months after effective date create a publically assessable websitesatisfactory to the Bank. | Due Date :04-Dec-2009
